<section class="about-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-heading">
      <h2 class="section-heading__title">{{ 'about.title' | t }}</h2>
      <p class="section-heading__subtitle">{{ 'about.subtitle' | t }}</p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-content">
      <h2>{{ 'about.story' | t }}</h2>
      <p>
        Aela Daily was born from a love for wabi-sabi &mdash; the Japanese philosophy of finding beauty in imperfection, impermanence, and simplicity. We believe that everyday objects should not just be functional, but also bring a sense of calm and mindfulness to your daily rituals.
      </p>
      <p>
        Each piece in our collection is thoughtfully curated or handcrafted, blending traditional craftsmanship with modern minimalist design. From handwoven rattan baskets to delicately scented soy wax sachets, every product tells a story of natural materials, skilled hands, and timeless aesthetics.
      </p>

      <h2>{{ 'about.mission' | t }}</h2>
      <p>
        Our mission is to bring the wabi-sabi spirit into homes across Europe. We source from artisans and suppliers who share our commitment to sustainability, quality, and ethical production. We prioritize natural, biodegradable materials and minimal packaging to reduce our environmental footprint.
      </p>
      <p>
        Whether you're creating a cozy corner, refreshing your home decor, or looking for the perfect thoughtful gift &mdash; Aela Daily is here to help you build a space that feels authentic, serene, and beautifully imperfect.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "About Content",
  "settings": []
}
{% endschema %}
